{"tid":2271471,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"賓州丟失三十萬張選票，視頻顯示大量被撕毀的投川普的選票","createTime":"2020-11-04T14:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T15:29:50.000Z","uid":293557,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"745e5dea9073bea1cc777552ae8124c8101441a6","tid":2271471,"uid":293557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"【美國大選】郵政署承認30萬張選票「不翼而飛」 涉12州包含搖擺州<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1915267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1915267&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2Fxu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=92688060\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1915267&h=52881874\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1915267</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter 短片<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/crystal78243104/status/1323986081881169920?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcrystal78243104%2Fstatus%2F1323986081881169920%3Fs%3D20&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2Fxu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=b97f0783\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcrystal78243104%2Fstatus%2F1323986081881169920%3Fs%3D20&h=5a9a87a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/crystal78243104/status/1323986081881169920?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨禁止有證件監票員入票站<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/IamMsFF/status/1323669290189529091?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIamMsFF%2Fstatus%2F1323669290189529091%3Fs%3D20&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2Fxu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=356711d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIamMsFF%2Fstatus%2F1323669290189529091%3Fs%3D20&h=08e3426a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/IamMsFF/status/1323669290189529091?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n美國郵政總局人員表示，大約有30萬張郵寄選票尚未掃描以便遞送，一名聯邦法官下令15州12個郵政區當天下午清理出這些選票，趕在投票所關閉前遞送，以確保沒有任何選票被延誤，但代表郵政總局的司法部律師在下午5點提出法律文件，表示郵政總局無法遵從法官的命令，堅持按照他們原先的查驗程序。原因是約有30萬張的選票「不翼而飛」，其中更包含著名搖擺州，亞利桑那州、佛州、喬治亞州、賓州、德州以及威斯康辛州等12個郵政區。<br />\n<br />\n美國郵政總局先前表示，過去5天以來選票送達的數量有所下降，粗估約缺失了30萬張票。美國華盛頓地區法官埃米特&bull;沙利文（Emmet Sullivan）則對此下令進行清查，並要求在美國時間3日3點半前完成。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，郵寄選票的準時性一直是大眾關注的問題，特別是在搖擺州地區，這些遲寄的選票很有可能會改變總統大選的結果；2016年總統大選時，以賓州地區來說每2張無效票當中就有一張是因為錯過截止日期遲寄。"},{"pid":"cc137d935bd981b685dee841e8220721735306ed","tid":2271471,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:34:56.000Z","msg":"係全美國的人選了習主席。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f6b248cd2a8d34380fdb106d73cf3098950403","tid":2271471,"uid":129068,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:35:11.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bfc2aa098dd984609e8c41af24c64a522c49d44","tid":2271471,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"假架"},{"pid":"66e0cbccc2a3821325898d0b2396d82f93f1e3e6","tid":2271471,"uid":6152,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:37:03.000Z","msg":"第一段fake 架"},{"pid":"17fdb970ced3895791f8457e0849e9efaee15479","tid":2271471,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:37:48.000Z","msg":"同香港一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國追香港追得好貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e052e70ca83c4bfec2877efe4e3be4ca7319174","tid":2271471,"uid":259120,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:41:52.000Z","msg":"殘體字tweets 唔好fol 咁貼"},{"pid":"40cc5f118ff90732417da23ee25b049b5762f8e8","tid":2271471,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"